#: walkasjesus_app/templates/law_of_messiah/listing.html:151
msgid ""
"Literally 'near to Israel' — non-Jewish believers who are deeply grafted "
"into the Messianic Jewish community and choose to embrace a Torah-informed "
"lifestyle."
msgstr ""
"Letterlijk 'dicht bij Israël' – niet-Joodse gelovigen die diep geënt zijn in"
